name: NBCNews
text:
RT @thereportnbc: Fmr. Atlanta police officer Garrett Rolfe faces 11 charges in the death of Rayshard Brooks. Police records show Rolfe had been previously reprimanded for his use of force in 2016. @PaulGerke reports.

Watch #TheEveningReport on @Quibi at the link. https://t.co/dEEpZ6Zgap https://t.co/ZtaBmVKsFv
